Simple app skeleton for Tiva C.

Generic funcationality:
 * main.c : initialization of console and logger and call to app entry point
 * event_logger.c : logger event formatting
 * uart_iface.c : write to UART serial ports

Apps: app_*.c

To build:
  * edit paths on top of makefile and 'make'

To write app to flash using OpenOCD:
    * Must have openocd.cfg and ek-tm4c123gxl.cfg in curr directory
    * $ openocd -f openocd.cfg -c program app_hwiswitask.out 0x00000000
